    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sections cut out of other works or documents; in art, primary examples are illuminations or other sections from a manuscript. For cuttings of newspapers and journals, use "clippings (information artifacts)." </Note_Text>
